results.description:
White Rock lake, Sunset Bay pier
Winter Cutie
These tiny cuties are everywhere right now.  Every winter they come here and eat the harvest of seeds.  Very cute with the bright spots of yellow under the wings and on their rump.  Love their nickname, butter butt.
